{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": null, "title": "Inbound SMS: Interacting with an Inbound SMS Campaign", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"inbound-sms-interacting-with-an-inbound-sms-campaign\">\n<h1>Inbound SMS: Interacting with an Inbound SMS Campaign<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#inbound-sms-interacting-with-an-inbound-sms-campaign\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">Inbound messaging starts with an individual sending a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/inbound_sms/trigger_term.html\">trigger term</a> to a program\u2019s number.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">This will enroll them in the SMS campaign\u2019s workflow.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">If this individual has an unknown phone number (meaning it is not associated with any contact in the Maha Platform), the Caller Identification service will search for a name to create a new contact.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">Once an inbound SMS campaign is activated, it will remain active until it is deactivated.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Campaigns</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Inbound SMS</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click on an inbound SMS campaign to view details, an audit trail, and comments</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and <strong>Deactivate Campaign</strong> or <strong>Activate Campaign</strong> to change the status of the campaign</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i>, <strong>Delete Campaign</strong>, and <strong>Yes</strong> to delete the campaign along with all associated workflows and performance data</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Design Workflow</strong> to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/design_a_workflow.html\">design</a> your inbound SMS campaign using the blocks below:</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_message_block.html\">Send Message</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/ask_question_block.html\">Ask Question</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/if_then_block.html\">If/Then</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/wait_block.html\">Wait</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_goal_block.html\">Set Goal</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_variable_block.html\">Set Variable</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/time_of_day_block.html\">Time of Day</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_property_block.html\">Update Property</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_consent_block.html\">Update Consent</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_lists_block.html\">Update Lists</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_topics_block.html\">Update Topics</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/enroll_in_a_workflow_block.html\">Enroll in Workflow</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_email_block.html\">Send Email</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_sms_block.html\">Send SMS</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_email_block.html\">Send Internal Email</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_sms_block.html\">Send Internal SMS</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Emails</strong> to click on the emails associated with the SMS campaign</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/inbound_sms/inbound_sms_campaign_performance.html\">Performance</a> to view recorded recipient interaction data</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "sourcename": "users/campaigns/guides/inbound_sms/inbound_SMS_campaigns.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Inbound SMS: Interacting with an Inbound SMS Campaign</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/campaigns/guides/inbound_sms/inbound_SMS_campaigns", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}